headlines.title: Baltic Dry Index Snaps 4-Day Rally
headlines.content_summary: The Baltic Exchange’s dry bulk index, which tracks rates for vessels transporting dry commodities, halted a four-day winning streak on Thursday, dropping 2.3% to 1,761 points, amid lower demand for larger vessels.
